      <title>在特朗普的关税之后，意大利银行削减了2025年的前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/bank-of-italy-cuts-2025-outlook-in-wake-of-trump-s-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利银行今年削减了对增长的预测，认为新的美国关税将阻止欧元区第三大经济体的扩张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/bank-of-italy-cuts-2025-outlook-in-wake-of-trump-s-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
