      <title>特朗普的关税引发了有关违反北约条约的辩论</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/trump-s-tariffs-spark-debate-on-possible-breach-of-nato-treaty</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）释放的一系列关税引发了北约成员的讨论，涉及这一举动是否违反了军事联盟的条约。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/trump-s-tariffs-spark-debate-on-possible-breach-of-nato-treaty</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 15:55:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
