    <item>
      <title>特朗普向鲍威尔施加压力，要求在讲话之前削减利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/trump-pressures-powell-to-slash-interest-rates-ahead-of-speech</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统呼吁美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔（Jerome Powell）削减利率，重申了他长期以来对中央银行渴望保持低价以保持消费者需求的渴望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/trump-pressures-powell-to-slash-interest-rates-ahead-of-speech</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 15:14:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Newsom说，加利福尼亚寻求盟友的关税豁免</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/newsom-says-california-ready-to-talk-with-trading-partners-m92wcdw0</link>
      <description><![CDATA[州长加文·纽瑟姆（Gavin Newsom）表示，他正在寻求对加利福尼亚制造产品的报复性关税的豁免，并希望与全球盟友就新的贸易关系进行谈判，这使该州成为反对唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的大量关税计划的后果的缓冲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/newsom-says-california-ready-to-talk-with-trading-partners-m92wcdw0</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 14:45:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普打入中国关税报复，说政策将继续</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/trump-says-policies-will-never-change-amid-tariff-fallout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统抨击了中国（China）对他的全面关税计划进行报复，并誓言他的经济政策“永远不会改变”，因为贸易战的前景对全球经济造成了更大的破坏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/trump-says-policies-will-never-change-amid-tariff-fallout</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 12:57:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加拿大欧洲呼吁普京回应美国停火计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/europe-canada-call-on-putin-to-respond-to-us-ceasefire-proposal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰的欧洲盟友和加拿大敦促俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京（Vladimir Putin）立即回应美国基辅（Kyiv）在没有条件的情况下接受的部分停火提案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/europe-canada-call-on-putin-to-respond-to-us-ceasefire-proposal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 08:27:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
